
## What is Hosting?

Hosting mhnje aapla website/project internet var upload karun dusryana access dya. Tumhi project tumchya laptop var banavla tari dusre lok baghu shakat nahi, tyasathi to "host" karava lagto.

------------------------------------------------------------

## Key Concepts

1. **Domain Name**
   - Domain mhnje website cha address (ud: epl.com, google.com).
   - Domain la .com, .org, .edu ashe extension astat.

2. **Hosting Platform**
   - Website che files store karun dusryana serve karnarya service la hosting platform mhantat.
   - Udaharan: Netlify, Vercel, Render, GitHub Pages, Firebase Hosting.

3. **Types of Hosting**
   - Static Hosting: Fakta HTML, CSS, JS asel tar.
   - Dynamic Hosting: Backend code (Node.js, Python, PHP) asel tar.

------------------------------------------------------------

## Hosting Process

1. Tumcha project build kara.
2. Hosting platform select kara.
3. Files upload kara (drag-and-drop, git, CLI).
4. Domain connect kara (optional).
5. Website live hoil, URL milto.

------------------------------------------------------------

## Example: Netlify var Static Site Hosting

1. [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/) var jaa.
2. Sign up kara, "Add new site" click kara.
3. Project folder drag-and-drop kara.
4. Netlify URL deto (ud: https://your-site.netlify.app).

------------------------------------------------------------

## Example: Render var Fullstack App Hosting

1. [Render](https://render.com/) var jaa.
2. Sign up kara, new web service create kara.
3. GitHub repo connect kara/ code upload kara.
4. Render build & deploy karto.
5. Live URL milto.

------------------------------------------------------------

## Summary Table

| Platform      | Static Hosting | Dynamic Hosting | Free Tier | Custom Domain |
|---------------|:-------------:|:--------------:|:---------:|:-------------:|
| Netlify       |      Yes      |      No        |   Yes     |     Yes       |
| Vercel        |      Yes      |     Limited    |   Yes     |     Yes       |
| Render        |      Yes      |      Yes       |   Yes     |     Yes       |
| GitHub Pages  |      Yes      |      No        |   Yes     |     Yes       |
| Firebase      |      Yes      |     Limited    |   Yes     |     Yes       |

------------------------------------------------------------


